text: Ak-Jar may refer to the following places in Kyrgyzstan: *Ak-Jar, At-Bashy, a village in At-Bashy District, Naryn Region *Ak-Jar, Kochkor, a village in Kochkor District, Naryn Region *Ak-Jar, Jalal-Abad, a village in Toktogul District, Jalal-Abad Region *Ak-Jar, Kara-Suu, a village in Kara-Suu District, Osh Region *Ak-Jar, Uzgen, a village in Uzgen District, Osh Region *Ak-Jar, Kara-Buura, a village in Kara-Buura District, Talas Region *Ak-Jar, Talas, a village in Talas District, Talas Region
title: Ak-Jar
